    <item>
      <title>贝索斯支持 AI 芯片制造商，市值 26 亿美元，与 Nvidia 竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jeff-bezos-is-betting-on-ai-chip-startup-tenstorrent-to-take-on-nvidia-nvda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司创始人杰夫·贝佐斯与三星联手以 7 亿美元收购 Tenstorrent，对这家志在与英伟达公司竞争的人工智能芯片初创公司的估值约为 26 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jeff-bezos-is-betting-on-ai-chip-startup-tenstorrent-to-take-on-nvidia-nvda</guid>
