    <item>
      <title>美国加强对中国获取人工智能内存和芯片工具的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-tightens-curbs-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-and-chips-tools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国公布了对中国获取芯片和人工智能关键零部件的新限制，进一步加大了遏制北京科技野心的力度，但没有采取早先提出的制裁更多中国关键企业的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-tightens-curbs-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-and-chips-tools</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
